            Welcome to the Tulare County Superior Court Web Page

                              Mission Statement

        To provide equal and timely access to justice, the impartial
   application of law and the promotion of community interventions toward
                the peaceful and fair resolution of disputes.

                   County Civic Center - 221 Mooney Blvd.

                         County Courthouse, Room 303

                           Visalia, CA 93291-4593

                             Phone 559-733-6561

    Hours of Operation:  8 AM to 5 PM - Monday through Friday (closed on
                               state holidays)

